ROC and Lift Curves

roc_curve <- xgb_final_fit %>% collect_predictions() %>% 
  roc_curve(truth=QO, .pred_1) %>% 
  autoplot()

lift_curve <- xgb_final_fit %>% collect_predictions() %>% 
  lift_curve(truth=QO, .pred_1) %>% 
  autoplot()

grid.arrange(roc_curve, lift_curve, ncol=2)
